    "description": "Bring the zing with black pepper and lemon-spiked chicken breast. Fry your coated chicken until golden then douse in a creamy garlic and oregano sauce and serve with mash and steamed veg. Now, that's what we call feel-good food. High in protein. Protein contributes to a growth in muscle mass.",
